{"id":619510,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】网民微信抱怨道路难走-称中国腐败/","date":"2019-10-09T06:42:17Z","modified":"2019-10-09T06:42:17Z","title":"【立此存照】网民微信抱怨道路难走 称中国“腐败国”遭举报被拘留","content":"<p>10月1日22时14分，在新中国成立70周年全国人民普天同庆之际，弥勒市公安局网安大队接到网民举报投诉，称有一网民多次辱国骂国，并截图了该网民辱骂内容的图片发到网警后台。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/8kaszimsu9r31.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-619514\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/8kaszimsu9r31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"449\" height=\"490\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/8kaszimsu9r31.jpg 449w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/8kaszimsu9r31-275x300.jpg 275w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/0feh9kmsu9r31.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619511\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/0feh9kmsu9r31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"449\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/0feh9kmsu9r31.jpg 443w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/0feh9kmsu9r31-270x300.jpg 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\" /></a></p>\n<p>经网警核实，被投诉网民真实姓名白某，系弥勒市竹园镇人。竹园派出所将白某传唤到案后，白某对自己违法行为供认不讳。</p>\n<p>目前，根据中华人民共和国《治安管理处罚法》第二十六条之规定，弥勒市公安局依法给予白某行政拘留五日的处罚。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5m0xlkmsu9r31.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-619515\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5m0xlkmsu9r31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"378\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5m0xlkmsu9r31.jpg 378w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/5m0xlkmsu9r31-167x300.jpg 167w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 378px) 100vw, 378px\" /></a></p>\n<p>警方提醒：网络非法外之地，网民在网络上必须遵守国家法律规定，不能因为泄私愤而发布辱国骂国言论，逞一时口快必将受到法律严惩。(文章来源：平安弥勒）</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e8%9c%97%e7%89%9b%e8%a1%8c%e8%b7%af%ef%bd%9c%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e8%be%b1%e5%9b%bd%e8%a8%80%e8%ae%ba%e3%80%81%e5%88%b6%e9%80%a0%e8%b0%a3%e8%a8%80/\">【立此存照】蜗牛行路｜发布辱国言论、制造谣言，三男子被拘！</a></p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E5%AE%BF%E8%BF%81%E7%BD%91%E6%B0%91%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E9%98%85%E5%85%B5%E5%BC%8F%E5%AE%98%E5%85%B5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%98-%E7%A7%B0%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5/\">【立此存照】宿迁网民侮辱阅兵式官兵被拘 称士兵被变成机器人</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%8d%97%e5%85%85%e9%98%86%e4%b8%ad%e7%bd%91%e8%ad%a6%e6%8b%98%e7%95%99%e4%b8%80%e4%be%ae%e8%be%b1%e9%98%85%e5%85%b5%e5%bc%8f%e5%ae%98%e5%85%b5/\">【立此存照】南充阆中网警拘留一”侮辱阅兵式官兵”网民</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e9%9e%8d%e5%b1%b1%e5%85%ac%e5%ae%89%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%80%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e5%85%ac%e7%84%b6%e4%be%ae%e8%be%b1%e9%98%85%e5%85%b5%e5%bc%8f%e5%ae%98/\">【立此存照】鞍山公安：一男子公然侮辱阅兵式 警方重拳出击</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e6%9c%80%e5%90%8e%e4%b8%80%e4%bd%8d%e7%81%ab%e7%ae%ad%e7%90%83%e8%bf%b7/\">【图说天朝】”中国最后一位火箭球迷”</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,38920],"tags":[38971,39070,39068,39069,39071,39048]}